OL,3,CAvanti 'told by watchdog' to cut the
OL,4,Cnumber of trains into Blackpool
OL,6,FTrain operator Avanti West Coast has
OL,7,Fconfirmed it is reducing its four
OL,8,Fdaily weekday services to and from
OL,9,FBlackpool to just one a day from next
OL,10,Fweek.
OL,12,FAmong the services which will no
OL,13,Flonger be available will be two direct
OL,14,Ftrains between London and the resort.
