OL,3,CAvanti 'told by watchdog' to cut the
OL,4,Cnumber of trains into Blackpool
OL,6,FThe move has been blasted by commuters
OL,7,Fbut Avanti says the decision lies with
OL,8,Fthe Office of Rail and Road (ORR) an
OL,9,Findependent, non-ministerial
OL,10,Fgovernment department aimed at
OL,11,Fprotecting rail users and regulating
OL,12,FNetwork Rail.
OL,14,FAvanti has expressed frustration with
OL,15,FORR for implementing the restrictions.
