OL,3,CAvanti 'told by watchdog' to cut the
OL,4,Cnumber of trains into Blackpool
OL,6,FAn Avanti West Coast spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are disappointed with the
OL,8,FOffice of Rail and Road's decision not
OL,9,Fto grant access rights from December
OL,10,Ffor four weekday services that we
OL,11,Fcurrently operate, including the 09:39
OL,12,FLondon to Blackpool North service, and
OL,13,Fthe 12:52 Blackpool North to London
OL,14,Fservice.
OL,16,F"This will clearly impact those
OL,17,Fcustomers who already use these
OL,18,Fservices.
