OL,3,CAvanti 'told by watchdog' to cut the
OL,4,Cnumber of trains into Blackpool
OL,6,F"However, we will still be delivering
OL,7,Feven more services across our network
OL,8,Ffrom the start of the December
OL,9,Ftimetable, including further
OL,10,Fadditional trains on our Liverpool
OL,11,Froute."
