OL,3,CAvanti 'told by watchdog' to cut the
OL,4,Cnumber of trains into Blackpool
OL,6,F"Places like Stirling, and Cleethorpes
OL,7,Fare getting brand new services to
OL,8,FLondon next week yet Blackpool is
OL,9,Fpaying the price and losing half of
OL,10,Fits service.
OL,12,F"The tax payer spent over #100m
OL,13,Felectrifying the Blackpool line with
OL,14,Fthe promise intercity trains would
OL,15,Freturn. Now , unsurprisingly, the
OL,16,Fservice is to be halved."
