OL,3,CAvanti 'told by watchdog' to cut the
OL,4,Cnumber of trains into Blackpool
OL,6,FAvanti says its London service to the
OL,7,FNorth West has been boosted, however,
OL,8,Fby ORR's decision to reinstate the
OL,9,Fcompany's 07:00 Manchester to London
OL,10,Fweekday service.
OL,12,FORR spokesperson said: "We recognise
OL,13,Fthat passengers will be disappointed
OL,14,Fthat these services will not be in the
OL,15,Ftimetable from December.
OL,17,F"In every timetable change, train
OL,18,Foperators bid to add or amend
OL,19,Fservices, and we are informed in our
OL,20,Fdecision making by what Network Rail
OL,21,Ftells us is possible.
