OL,3,CAvanti 'told by watchdog' to cut the
OL,4,Cnumber of trains into Blackpool
OL,6,F"In this case, Network Rail provided
OL,7,Fevidence and recommended that ORR
OL,8,Fdecline the applications to secure
OL,9,Fbetter reliability on the network as a
OL,10,Fwhole.
OL,12,F"We would welcome the opportunity to
OL,13,Fwork with Network Rail and train
OL,14,Foperators should they consider that
OL,15,Fthere is room for these services in
OL,16,Ffuture timetables."
